  "designMd": "# Design System — Lando\n\n> Extracted from [https://landonorris.com/](https://landonorris.com/)\n> Generated by Ditto on April 9, 2026\n\n## 1. Visual Theme & Atmosphere\n\nThe design follows a **light theme** with a clean, light background (`#f4f4ed`). The primary accent color is a **light lime** (`#d2ff00`) used for interactive elements and brand moments.\n\nTypography is built on **Mona Sans Variable** for headings and **Brier** for body text, creating a balanced dual-family system.\n\n**Key Characteristics:**\n- Light background (`#f4f4ed`) with dark text (`#535450`)\n- Primary accent: `#d2ff00`\n- Font: Mona Sans Variable (headings) / Brier (body)\n- Border radius: 7.2px – 14px\n- Heading weight: 800, Body weight: 400\n\n## 2. Color Palette & Roles\n\n### Primary\n- **Light Lime** (`#d2ff00`): Primary brand color, CTAs, interactive highlights — 19 occurrences\n\n### Secondary\n- **Lime** (`#b2c73a`): Secondary accent, supporting elements — 19 occurrences\n\n### Background\n- **Light Gray** (`#f4f4ed`): Page background — 322 occurrences\n\n### Surface\n- **White** (`#ffffff`): Card/container background, elevated surfaces\n\n### Text Primary\n- **Charcoal** (`#535450`): Primary heading and body text — 141 occurrences\n\n### Text Secondary\n- **Dark Lime** (`#282c20`): Secondary text, descriptions — 104 occurrences\n\n### Text Muted\n- **Black** (`#111112`): Muted text, placeholders, captions — 22 occurrences\n\n### Border\n- **Gray** (`#dde1d2`): Standard borders, dividers — 128 occurrences\n\n### Neutral\n- **Lime** (`#b4b8a5`): Neutral/utility color — 80 occurrences\n\n\n## 3. Typography Rules\n\n### Font Family\n- **Heading**: Mona Sans Variable, fallback: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif\n- **Body**: Brier, fallback: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif\n- **Monospace**: ui-monospace, fallback: ui-monospace, monospace\n\n### Hierarchy\n\n| Role | Font | Size | Weight | Line Height | Letter Spacing |\n|------|------|------|--------|-------------|----------------|\n| H1 | Mona Sans Variable | 38px | 700 | 44px | normal |\n| H2 | Mona Sans Variable | 32px | 700 | 36px | normal |\n| H3 | Mona Sans Variable | 12px | 600 | 15px | normal |\n| Body | Mona Sans Variable | 16.6667px | 400 | 20.8333px | normal |\n| Small | Mona Sans Variable | 14px | 400 | 1.4 | normal |\n| Caption | Mona Sans Variable | 8.33333px | 400 | 1.4 | normal |\n\n### Principles\n- Heading weight: **800**\n- Body weight: **400**\n- Base size: 16.6667px\n- Line height: tight (1.15), normal (1.5), relaxed (1.75)\n\n## 4. Component Stylings\n\n### Buttons\n\n**Primary**\n- Background: `#d2ff00`\n- Text: `#535450`\n- Padding: 0px\n- Radius: 7.2px\n- Font: 16.6667px Brier weight 400\n\n### Cards & Containers\n- Background: `#ffffff`\n- Border: 1px solid `#dde1d2`\n- Radius: 14px\n- Shadow: `0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)`\n\n### Inputs & Forms\n- Background: `#f4f4ed`\n- Border: 1px solid `#dde1d2`\n- Radius: 7.2px\n- Focus: 1px solid `#d2ff00`\n- Text: `#535450`\n- Placeholder: `#111112`\n\n\n## 5. Layout Principles\n\n### Spacing System\n- Scale: 4.16667px, 8.33333px, 13.3333px, 16.6667px, 33.3333px, 50px, 63px, 75.78px, 80px, 113.125px, 130.312px, 160px\n- XS: 4.16667px, SM: 8.33333px, MD: 16.6667px, LG: 16.6667px, XL: 33.3333px\n\n### Border Radius Scale\n- Small: 7.2px\n- Medium: 7.2px\n- Large: 14px\n- Full: 9999px\n\n### Grid\n- Max content width: ~1200px\n- Standard section padding: 33.3333px – 50px\n\n## 6. Depth & Elevation\n\n| Level | Treatment | Use |\n|-------|-----------|-----|\n| Subtle | `0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05)` | Hover hints, small cards |\n| Standard | `0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)` | Cards, dropdowns |\n| Elevated | `0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)` | Modals, popovers |\n\n## 7. Do's and Don'ts\n\n### Do\n- Use `#d2ff00` as the primary interactive/CTA color\n- Use `#535450` for headings, `#282c20` for body\n- Keep border-radius consistent: 7.2px – 14px\n- Use Mona Sans Variable for headings at weight 800\n- Apply shadows from the elevation scale for depth\n- Use `#dde1d2` for all standard borders\n\n### Don't\n- Don't use pure black (#000000) for text — use `#535450`\n- Don't mix border-radius sizes inconsistently\n- Don't use colors outside the defined palette\n- Don't use font weights not present in the type scale\n- Don't skip the spacing scale — use the defined values\n\n## 8. Responsive Behavior\n\n### Breakpoints\n| Name | Width | Key Changes |\n|------|-------|-------------|\n| Mobile | <640px | Single column, reduced heading sizes |\n| Tablet | 640-1024px | 2-column grids, moderate padding |\n| Desktop | 1024-1280px | Full layout |\n| Large Desktop | >1280px | Centered content with generous margins |\n\n### Collapsing Strategy\n- Navigation: horizontal links → hamburger menu\n- Feature cards: multi-column → single column stacked\n- Typography scale compresses ~20% on mobile\n- Spacing reduces proportionally\n\n## 9. Agent Prompt Guide\n\n### Quick Color Reference\n- Primary CTA: `#d2ff00`\n- Background: `#f4f4ed`\n- Surface: `#ffffff`\n- Heading text: `#535450`\n- Body text: `#282c20`\n- Muted text: `#111112`\n- Border: `#dde1d2`\n- Success: `#22c55e`\n- Warning: `#f59e0b`\n- Error: `#ef4444`\n\n### Quick Typography Reference\n- Heading: Mona Sans Variable, weight 800\n- Body: Brier, weight 400\n- Mono: ui-monospace\n- Base size: 16.6667px\n\n### Example Component Prompts\n- \"Create a hero section: background `#f4f4ed`, headline at 38px Mona Sans Variable weight 800, color `#535450`. Subtitle at 1.125rem weight 400, color `#282c20`. Primary button (`#d2ff00`, 7.2px, white text) and ghost button (transparent, 1px solid `#dde1d2`, `#d2ff00` text).\"\n- \"Design a card: `#ffffff` background, 1px solid `#dde1d2`, 14px radius. Shadow: `0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)`. Title at 1.25rem weight 800, `#535450`. Body at 16.6667px weight 400, `#282c20`.\"\n\n### Iteration Guide\n1. Always use the defined color palette — no ad-hoc colors\n2. Heading weight is 800, body weight is 400\n3. Border radius: 7.2px (small), 7.2px (default), 14px (large)\n4. Use the spacing scale: xs(4.16667px), sm(8.33333px), md(16.6667px), lg(16.6667px), xl(33.3333px)\n5. Shadow levels: sm, md, lg — use consistently",
